snippet.textDisplay: Hey guys. Thanks for listening. Didn't say you all had to do this for free. I'm not sure the fans are too happy they are being charged for something they asked for but oh well. I'll make an offer you can't refuse. At the right time of course. When gaming regulations hit, I'll have something figured out for both developer and consumer. Great direct. As always, I'm just an avid fan. Thanks for benefiting off my image and name but you guys earned it. Especially with the Super Mario Sunshine fiasco. The letter PI isn't free. Even if you do let it go on indefinitely and pass the results from one generation to the next, and get something else that wasn't numbers. Anyway, I hope you enjoy your day. Cheers.
